      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Add provider label metadata characterization tests",
        "body": "This adds no-behavior-change characterization coverage for provider label metadata as a first step toward #804.\n\nThe new tests document structural expectations for current `ProviderMetadata` labels without renaming providers, changing UI text, or deciding the final naming convention:\n\n* `displayName` is non-empty for every provider\n* `sessionLabel` is non-empty for every provider\n* empty `weeklyLabel` providers are explicitly characterized\n* `supportsOpus` providers declare a non-empty `opusLabel`\n* `opusLabel` is either nil or non-empty\n\nCurrent behavior is preserved, including the existing Mistral empty `weeklyLabel` exception.\n\nValidation:\n\n* `./Scripts/lint.sh lint`\n* `swift test --filter ProviderLabelMetadataCharacterizationTests`\n* `swift test --filter ProviderRegistryTests`\n\nThis does not close #804; it is an inventory/characterization first step only.",
